#: ../../../components/http_foundation/session_php_bridge.rst:44
msgid ""
"Symfony sessions store data like attributes in special 'Bags' which use a"
" key in the ``$_SESSION`` superglobal. This means that a Symfony session "
"cannot access arbitrary keys in ``$_SESSION`` that may be set by the "
"legacy application, although all the ``$_SESSION`` contents will be saved"
